&lt;p&gt;Our responsibility is to keep clinicians productive, supported, and paid for their time. Patient cancellations, refusals, and schedule changes happen in home health. Your paycheck should not have to suffer because of them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If your day runs longer, you are paid for the additional time worked. If you work efficiently and finish early, your guaranteed daily pay remains the same.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How Health Link Supports Clinicians&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dedicated scheduling team to help coordinate visits and keep your day organized&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clinical coordination support for physician communication, orders, and follow-up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Authorization and DME support so you can stay focused on patient care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI-assisted documentation technology designed to reduce charting time and after-hours paperwork&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI-assisted route planning and territory management designed to reduce unnecessary drive time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company vehicle available to reduce wear and tear on your personal vehicle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong referral volume and stable local caseloads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsive clinical leadership and 24-hour clinical support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full benefits package&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We believe a full-time job should fit into an 8-hour workday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active California Physical Therapist License&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid driver&#39;s license&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Home health experience preferred, but not required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why Health Link&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more than 20 years, Health Link Home Health has served patients throughout the Bay Area and built a reputation for&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;clinical excellence, responsive service, and strong patient outcomes&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Health Link has maintained&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Medicare&#39;s highest 5-Star Quality Rating&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;while consistently delivering outstanding patient outcomes, including&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;rehospitalization rates below industry averages.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Health Link Home Health is an Equal Opportunity Employer.&lt;/p&gt;

